description: Lists all tags on an Amazon Neptune resource.

parameters.name: ResourceName
parameters.description: The Amazon Neptune resource with tags to be listed. This value is an Amazon Resource Name (ARN). For information about creating an ARN, see Constructing an Amazon Resource Name (ARN).

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: This parameter is not currently supported. (dict) --- This type is not currently supported. (string) ---

nested_params.name: Name
nested_params.description: This parameter is not currently supported.

nested_params.name: Values
nested_params.description: This parameter is not currently supported.

nested_items.name: TagList
nested_items.description: List of tags returned by the ListTagsForResource operation.

nested_items.name: Key
nested_items.description: A key is the required name of the tag. The string value can be from 1 to 128 Unicode characters in length and can't be prefixed with aws: or rds:. The string can only contain the set of Unicode letters, digits, white-space, --_', --.', --/', --=', --+', ---' (Java regex: '^([\p{L}\p{Z}\p{N}_.:/=+\-]*)$').

nested_items.name: Value
nested_items.description: A value is the optional value of the tag. The string value can be from 1 to 256 Unicode characters in length and can't be prefixed with aws: or rds:. The string can only contain the set of Unicode letters, digits, white-space, --_', --.', --/', --=', --+', ---' (Java regex: '^([\p{L}\p{Z}\p{N}_.:/=+\-]*)$').
